race.comment: LIMOSA (11) looks close to a win. Just missed over a similar trip two back then stepped out over further last time and was well off best. Finds a lesser maiden this time and will be hard to hold out. SIAM EMERALD (6) has been racing in richer maidens as well, the latest finding the line strongly to finish runner-up. Overdue and looks a top chance. IDLING BEHIND (10) turned in an eye-catching run when getting beyond 2000m latest, just missing over 2200m at Ararat. Would go close here with a repeat of that figure. GOTTACOOKACURRY (7) has had three runs so far and yet to feature but looks as though the extra ground will suit. Should be an improver.
